24.667 20.333 43.667 41 57 7.333 4.667 11\n10.667 11 18 0 6-1 10-3 12s-6.667 5-14 9c-28.667 14.667-53.667 35.667-75 63\n-1.333 1.333-3.167 3.5-5.5 6.5s-4 4.833-5 5.5c-1 .667-2.5 1.333-4.5 2s-4.333 1\n-7 1c-4.667 0-9.167-1.833-13.5-5.5S337 184 337 178c0-12.667 15.667-32.333 47-59\nH213l-171-1c-8.667-6-13-12.333-13-19 0-4.667 4.333-11.333 13-20h359\nc-16-25.333-24-45-24-59z'/></svg></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> is the <strong>eigenvector</strong></li>\n<li><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>λ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\lambda</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">λ</span></span></span></span> is the <strong>eigenvalue</strong></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"eigenvalues"}}